additional_notes: Panels with non-standard thicknesses are available upon request with previous agreement on minimum quantities. Other films are available on request. Dryfix, (product name is inspired by its properties: fixing dry and safe) without holes can connect tiles, plates, solar thermal panels or photovoltaic modules. It does not need screws, bolts, rivets, self-drilling screws with rubber seals.
